brat curation and correction related classes

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationOption
    This class comprises instances of AnnotationSelection, each representing a possible choice of disagreeing annotation sets.
    AnnotationSelection
    This class comprises usernames, which agree on a specific annotation (same annotation type, same annotation value, same position).
    CasDiff
    Class for finding clusters of equal annotations.
    CompareResult
    Contains agreements and differences as the result of the Method CasDiff.compareFeatureFS().
    DoubleIterator<A extends org.apache.uima.cas.text.AnnotationFS,B extends org.apache.uima.cas.text.AnnotationFS>
    If you put in two lists of AnnotationFS, it will get all the pairs that overlap in some way.
  • Exception Summary
